      <h2>Discharge disposition</h2>
            
      <div>
              
        <p>This value set defines a set of codes that can be used to where the patient left the hospital.</p>

            
      </div>
            
      <p>This code system http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/discharge-disposition defines the following codes:</p>
            
